{
  "bookId": "heshanggong-laozi",
  "num": 60,
  "title": "第六十章（居位）",
  "author": "老子",
  "authorId": "Laozi",
  "dynasty": "周",
  "era": "周",
  "genre": "prose",
  "verses": [
    {
      "text": "治大國者若烹小鮮。"
    },
    {
      "text": "以道蒞天下，其鬼不神。"
    },
    {
      "text": "非其鬼不神，其神不傷人。"
    },
    {
      "text": "非其神不傷人，聖人亦不傷。"
    },
    {
      "text": "夫兩不相傷，"
    },
    {
      "text": "故德交歸焉。"
    }
  ],
  "sections": {},
  "annotations": [],
  "layers": {
    "heshanggong": [
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-1",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 9
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "鮮，魚。 烹小魚不去腸、不去鱗、不敢撓，恐其糜也。 治國煩則下亂，治身煩則精散。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-2",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 1,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 11
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "以道德居位治天下，則鬼不敢以其精神犯人也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-3",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 2,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 12
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "其鬼非無精神也，非不入正，不能傷自然之人。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-4",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 3,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 13
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "非鬼神不能傷害人。以聖人在位不傷害人，故鬼不敢干之也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-5",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 4,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 6
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "鬼與聖人俱兩不相傷也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-6",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 5,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 6
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "夫兩不相傷，則人得治於陽，鬼神得治於陰，人得保全其性命，鬼得保其精神，故德交歸焉。",
        "source": "cham"
      }
    ]
  },
